## About _Netflixify App_

This video streaming application is a enables users to browse a categorized film library, perform instant searches, stream movies with adaptive quality based on internet speed, manage favorites, track view counts, and authenticate via Google OAuth.

- Browse a categorized library of films.
- Search for movies live and easy access for any movie.
- Stream videos with multiple quality options, encoded for adaptive playback.
- Adjust video quality dynamically based on internet speed or manually by the user.
- Add movies to a favorites list for quick access.
- Track view counts for each film.
- Log in securely using Google account authentication.


## Control Panel
- Access a comprehensive control panel for app management.
- Fully manage movie categories (add, edit, delete, search, export data).
- Fully manage movies (add, edit, delete, search, export data).
  - Upload movies and details to the app.
  - Encode uploaded movies into multiple quality levels.
  - Track the movie encoding progress
  - Edit and delete movies as needed.
  - control publish and unpublish movies after encoding complete.
- Fully manage roles and permissions (view, add, edit, delete, search, export data).
- Fully manage admins (add, edit, delete, search, export data).
- Define admin roles and permissions for access control.
- List admins that linked on role.
- Fully manage customers (add, edit, delete, search, export data).
- Oversee app settings from a centralized dashboard.